def solve():
    N = int(input())
    mochi = [int(input()) for _ in range(N)]
    mochi.sort(reverse=True)
    count = 1
    for i in range(1, N):
        if mochi[i] < mochi[i-1]:
            break
        count += 1
    print(count)
